Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.39,0:00:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒不了…你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.40,0:00:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒不…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.84,0:00:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.58,0:00:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒不了…你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.39,0:00:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(化貓)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.55,0:01:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(物怪)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.86,0:01:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清冷的月光照着你徘徊的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.53,0:01:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想說的話卻說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.60,0:01:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日子令人如此不耐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.51,0:01:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猶記那虛偽的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.01,0:01:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘卻那溫暖的淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.38,0:01:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那雙失了魂的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.12,0:01:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,映照着什麼樣的風景？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.22,0:01:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虛幻的下弦月隱臟於雲間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.10,0:01:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗如今正慢慢浮現
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.06,0:02:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,述說着真相
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.07,0:02:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁抱着孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.80,0:02:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚是否又將對月長嘆…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.48,0:02:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(第一幕)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在此迎接福壽站地鐵開通之日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.96,0:02:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人感到非常榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.13,0:02:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.06,0:02:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.87,0:02:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市長先生，請準備一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.07,0:02:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.57,0:02:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家…謝謝大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝…謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.65,0:02:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒抽中的人請退到後面\N請退到後面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘車時務必出示您的中獎單
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.45,0:02:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要推擠…請不要推擠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:02:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.06,0:03:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…第四車廂是在這裡等嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.06,0:03:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.53,0:03:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不是耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.94,0:03:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是第一車廂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有相關人員才能搭乘喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.81,0:03:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的車廂在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼遠啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.91,0:03:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,0:03:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭\N行李那麼大會造成別人困擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過他長得還滿帥的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣東西的人還真辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.52,0:03:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說啊謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.09,0:03:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思借過一下，借過一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借過一下…借過一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往後退，請往後退
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.97,0:03:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬歲…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.48,0:03:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思借過一下\N借過，借過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:03:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.95,0:04:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市長的安全就拜託您了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.52,0:04:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.03,0:04:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市長好賊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.67,0:04:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想坐那邊的車廂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.63,0:04:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…中午前就能回來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.77,0:04:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在第四站地鐵就會折返
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.44,0:04:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概一個小時就會回到這囉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，準備正式發車！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.85,0:04:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有四分鐘！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.86,0:04:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市民也對此翹首以盼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望二期工程能夠盡快進行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.03,0:04:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.20,0:04:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都是靠市長先生的幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.10,0:04:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後也請您多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.67,0:04:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是每朝日報的森谷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜地鐵順利開通
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問市長您現在的心情如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.34,0:04:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠不負所有市民的期望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.18,0:05:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能用\N“無限感動”這句話來形容
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.75,0:05:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市長你太客氣了，太客氣了\N哼，這隻老狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，那邊那個記者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.95,0:05:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問到這裡就好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.76,0:05:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬歲…萬歲…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到車子能在地下行走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.10,0:05:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直像做夢一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.63,0:05:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.63,0:05:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是要拿到車票就很辛苦喲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，真的花了不少工夫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬歲…萬歲…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.78,0:07:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出意外了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停車…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.88,0:07:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家冷靜點！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.95,0:07:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕！好可怕哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.35,0:07:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰誰來幫我一下啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.42,0:08:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.38,0:08:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我多慮了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.21,0:08:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市長先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人呢？消失到哪去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.22,0:08:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.32,0:08:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不曉得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.22,0:08:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊剛才真是太謝謝您了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.06,0:08:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.26,0:08:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.09,0:08:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…在此向各位乘客報告
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.60,0:08:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為方才於列車行進軌道上\N發現障礙物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.20,0:08:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.97,0:08:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此緊急將電車停下來\N第一車廂喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.44,0:08:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過目前障礙物已移除\N是第一車廂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.51,0:08:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電車將繼續行駛\N喂，你們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.54,0:08:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.21,0:08:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉給各位帶來困擾\N沒必要這樣大聲嚷嚷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.55,0:08:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣對女士很沒禮貌哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.95,0:09:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.15,0:09:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰也無法解釋這麼離奇的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.82,0:09:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我我要回原來的座位去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.05,0:09:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這麼重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.48,0:09:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全打不開
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.58,0:09:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊讓我試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.25,0:09:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法啊女人這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是駕駛艙的木下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車掌室請回答
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.24,0:09:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個老頭\N還真會搶鋒頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:09:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.81,0:09:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.61,0:10:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不開車呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.75,0:10:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，我說你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在幹嘛呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.55,0:10:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.09,0:10:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來得請他們改進這些車廂門
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.85,0:10:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓女士也能方便打開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.66,0:10:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他車廂呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.38,0:10:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…痛哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.75,0:10:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.42,0:10:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市長先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.76,0:10:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰在開車啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.73,0:11:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒不了…你！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳剛剛…有說\N“饒不了你”嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.78,0:11:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳剛剛是不是說了\N“饒不了你”？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人…說嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.43,0:12:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是我聽錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭，好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.40,0:12:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽錯了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.04,0:12:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這輛電車
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不聽你的使喚啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.51,0:12:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經用盡所有辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.28,0:12:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒辦法跟地上取得聯繁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.78,0:12:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這輩子完了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.52,0:12:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易有這個難得的機會…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為一直待在隧道裡的關係，…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.79,0:12:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然捲入這種意外\N我的聽力也變怪怪的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.49,0:12:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上午十點五分，緊急停車
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.99,0:12:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘客消失，原因不明\N可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.40,0:12:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說，記者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方邊看書寫字
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.34,0:12:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你頭不會暈嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯我幹這工作已經有二十年了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.77,0:12:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就習以為常了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.11,0:12:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小弟弟你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.38,0:12:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別嚇人好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.22,0:12:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…剛才那邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.49,0:13:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.07,0:13:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.34,0:13:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣東西的先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記者！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.54,0:13:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.09,0:13:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.43,0:13:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個奇怪的街頭藝人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是從哪裡進來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如各位所見\N是從隔壁車廂走過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼我只是個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣藥的喲！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.48,0:13:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時代不打扮成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.55,0:13:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藥可是很難賣出去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此…也太華麗了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.45,0:14:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該也看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.42,0:14:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道什麼原因…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.66,0:14:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們…似乎無法走出這扇門
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.63,0:14:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且剛剛市長…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.23,0:14:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還從這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.63,0:14:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.44,0:14:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂別在那瞎猜行不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電車自已繼續行駛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.41,0:14:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.61,0:14:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被狐狸精迷上似的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.98,0:14:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是狐狸所為哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.49,0:14:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不過是形容詞而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.99,0:14:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市長他…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.06,0:14:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被物怪殺死的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.49,0:14:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.46,0:14:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.27,0:14:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.10,0:14:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了，很可怕耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.67,0:14:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說夢話等睡着時再說吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.47,0:14:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是意外啦，意外
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是電車自已開動…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.61,0:14:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是故障了嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.24,0:14:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在大呼小叫了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:15:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情發生時你根本沒看到嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.11,0:15:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.12,0:15:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.52,0:15:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽屜自已打開了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.14,0:15:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…天秤喲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.64,0:15:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從它傾斜的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.38,0:15:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以得知…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.55,0:15:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物怪的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在座所有人都與物怪有關
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物怪將所有相關之人\N都聚集在這節車廂裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.11,0:16:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有關…\N我們可都是第一次見面喲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊\N我們都是幸運抽到車票而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.05,0:16:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說有什麼關係啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.58,0:16:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此事\N我想各位心裡應該很清楚才是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.19,0:16:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.99,0:16:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認識其中一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.09,0:16:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.76,0:16:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也覺得他很面熟…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.03,0:16:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中一個人的話，我也想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.53,0:16:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.37,0:16:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.24,0:16:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我誰也不認識啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.34,0:16:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是完全搞不清楚狀況…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔~六個人中\N有四個人認識同一個人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能請各位再說詳細點嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是一點印象也沒有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.49,0:16:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從最旁邊的人開始報上\N自已的姓名，年齡，職業
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有在哪見過我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.66,0:16:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯.就是這種語氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.00,0:17:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是野本千代，今年二十一歲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.30,0:17:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在車站前的咖啡廳當女侍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.03,0:17:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,職業婦女中的當紅職業啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.07,0:17:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦~大概是這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.41,0:17:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別岔開話題\N我可是從沒去過咖啡廳哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.44,0:17:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是這樣，刑警先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.54,0:17:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是曾到我店裡\N打聽過消息嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.65,0:17:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.21,0:17:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔~三，四個月前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.02,0:17:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？妳怎麼知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.42,0:17:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刑警先生跟他的屬下\N也曾出現在我家門口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後一直在門口抽煙\N你忘了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.39,0:17:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，我叫山口晴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是專職的家庭主婦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾歲？\N你很沒禮貌耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三十五歲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.67,0:17:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧我還替妳掩飾呢~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.13,0:17:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼您先生呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.14,0:17:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年前因肺病去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.51,0:17:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在跟婆婆住在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.51,0:17:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說這些無關緊要的事！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.01,0:17:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刑警先生你真的沒印象嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟妳不一樣，我可是很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪可能把每件事都記下來啊\N快點繼續吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.15,0:17:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治療健忘的藥…\N我說刑警先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.19,0:17:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自已都還沒說自已的\N姓名和年齡呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.42,0:17:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呿，真是脾氣不好的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.26,0:18:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫門脇榮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.32,0:18:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年四十歲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是南分局的刑警
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.26,0:18:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給你個提示好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.10,0:18:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是常來我店裡的女熟客
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.70,0:18:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是現在當紅的“摩登女郎”\N(摩登女郎即時髦女性)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.47,0:18:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還不只這樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.63,0:18:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以說是常做男裝打扮的美女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一直閃爍着耀眼的高貴光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.21,0:18:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是聽說她卻不幸被列車輾死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.08,0:18:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是故意要輾死她的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.45,0:18:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是故意的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每朝日報…火車…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.53,0:18:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯\N當時駕駛那輛列車的就是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得你的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.46,0:18:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木下文平，二十八歲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.47,0:18:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她自已從天橋跳下來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時就已經摔死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.54,0:18:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我駕駛的列車\N只是剛好經過那裡罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.01,0:18:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳下來？\N更何況我事後才知道那是個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.04,0:18:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦，冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:18:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個案子已經以自殺結案了\N原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.62,0:19:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你臉色不太好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.02,0:19:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要來點安神的藥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.72,0:19:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.96,0:19:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.39,0:19:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫森谷清
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.03,0:19:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是報社的總編輯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.46,0:19:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為今天人手不足
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.13,0:19:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才親自出來採訪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.70,0:19:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個事件的死者\N就是這個人的屬下喲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.44,0:19:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說，那個人是女記者囉？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.57,0:19:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她連名字都很時髦呢\N我記得是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.48,0:19:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得很清楚喲\N市川節子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.05,0:19:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是漢字組成的名字\N真令人羡慕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.48,0:19:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這其中一定有什麼誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.05,0:19:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我誰都不認識啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.52,0:19:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要被困在這裡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.06,0:19:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點放我出去啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.56,0:19:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.40,0:19:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.23,0:19:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小弟弟，你叫什麼名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小林正男
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.57,0:19:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唸哪所學校呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.70,0:19:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛從小學畢業
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.44,0:19:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在幫人家送牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.71,0:19:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早就要起來\N很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.31,0:19:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:20:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來列車通過那兒的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.41,0:20:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像也是早上五點左右
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.48,0:20:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在霧原陸橋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.08,0:20:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你送牛奶的時候會經過嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯會經過…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.66,0:20:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關係都連在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.52,0:20:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.46,0:20:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.29,0:20:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時那邊站了一個抱着貓的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.21,0:21:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化貓啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.71,0:21:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(待續)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.55,0:21:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當你不在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.22,0:21:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就無法笑得開懷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.09,0:21:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這平凡的街道上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.39,0:21:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是如此地被你吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.00,0:21:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能將那些無可取代的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好珍惜並活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.51,0:21:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也別無所求
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.79,0:21:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盛開在那片天空下的夏之花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.83,0:22:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨風緩緩飄落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.30,0:22:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星光落在早已看不見的夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.68,0:22:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那段日子\N將是我此生無可比喻的珍愛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
